{"id":174580,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":1,"day":10}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"226","ytitle":"","mtitle":"春联试拟","ftitle":"","authors":["吕华田"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吕华田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开经济斗争，有困难；有办法；有希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加强政治学习，爱科学；爱劳动；爱人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳粮税，确保军事胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买公债，解决财政困难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开大竞买，买储公债，从事国家建设。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决一面倒，倒向苏联，保卫世界和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国土数万里，到处解放歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公债两亿分，一片认购热潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(五)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来买，我来买，争购公债。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男也忙，女也忙，努力生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(六)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年财政，究竟如何?有困难；有办法；有希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四亿七千万人民，应该怎样?齐学习；齐节约；齐生产。"}]}